com.webgeoservices.multisearch.configs

Class ConfigParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.webgeoservices.multisearch.configs.ConfigParams

  • public class ConfigParams
extends java.lang.Object
    ConfigParams class provides a way to pass additional parameters such as countries, search types and language to the ProviderConfig class.
